seo_en: Batch URL probing,basic information of URL,status code,title,server,content length
summary: 该插件用于获取指定URL的基本信息，包括状态码、标题、服务器类型和内容长度，以检测URL的活跃情况。
summary_en: This plugin is used to obtain the basic information of specified URLs, including status code, title, server type, and content length, to detect the activity of URLs.
